headline: How UnitedHealthcare and other insurers use AI to deny claims
summary: The fatal shooting of UnitedHealthcare (UNH) CEO Brian Thompson on Wednesday has sparked public scrutiny of health insurers, especially regarding their use of AI in evaluating claims. The incident also comes as several insurance providers have been facing litigation over their coverage practices and the potential impact they have on patient care.
